def cmp(a, b):  # Compare two tuples based on the first element in descending order
    if a[0] > b[0]:
        return -1
    elif a[0] < b[0]:
        return 1
    else:
        if a[1] < b[1]:
            return -1
        elif a[1] > b[1]:
            return 1
        else:
            return 0
